title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 10PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday evening’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 10PM” game were:
6-9-4-8
(six, nine, four, eight)
